347
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:02,790
What should you do?

348
00:25:04,070 --> 00:25:04,880
That's right.

349
00:25:07,000 --> 00:25:07,790
Mr. Ma,

350
00:25:08,140 --> 00:25:09,200
